{
  "stem": "27747.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So all Jews-- all Jews and all Poles have to leave the eastern part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ukraine and Polesia and [POLISH]-- all those parts had to be cleared of Jews and repatriated to the new Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, their Poland was also influenced by them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was really under their auspices, but it was called the new Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by trains we were taken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I left with the family together, with the-- with the family [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Gelman ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and the way in Rowne, the train stopped and then other Jews joined us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where the Poles traveled, I was not with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I have never met again the Polish family, but they, too, repatriated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They repatriated to close to the town where we landed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We landed in Bytom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Many Jews settled in the Lodz, and Lodz had a committee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the committee was-- had a lot of, you know, registered Jews-- whoever was from the outskirts of Poland and the survivors.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Bytom, we heard that [POLISH], my friend from home, has arrived to Lodz, an in Lodz he heard that we are in Bytom.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he and his brother Harvey-- at that time he was [POLISH]-- and his-- and his-- and his wife.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was Russian-born Jewish lady.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came to Bytom to look for us and they settled in Bytom also.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course it was good to see my boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He taught me how to ski and-- and-- and-- and ice skate and bicycle-ride.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to school together, but since he was two years older, so he was in-- in higher grades than I was, also in the [INAUDIBLE] school.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
